CHANGES IN VERSION 1.0-3
----------------------

BUG FIXES

    o We have fixed some bugs regarding C language programming.


IMPROVEMENTS SINCE LAST TIME
----------------------

    o We have refined some of the code to speed up the package.


----------------------
FUTURE DEVELOPMENT
----------------------

    o We intend to make some refinements to the package by introducing better S4 classes and methods.
    o We will add more distributions to the package including Generalized Gamma and Gompertz.
    o Since we are working on length-biased models, these models will be added to the package.

